        <level>
          <content>
            <p><b>Subject matter and legislative competence of devolved legislatures</b></p>
          </content>
        </level>
        <paragraph>
          <num>50 </num>
          <content>
            <p>There is no matter in the Act that is within the legislative competence of the devolved legislatures.</p>
          </content>
        </paragraph>
      </section>
